@* ===========================================================================
   File        : LoginLayout.razor
   Namespace   : AbsenceApp.Client.Framework.Layout
   Author      : Michael
   Version     : 3.0.0
   Created     : 2026-03-17
   Updated     : 2026-04-07
   ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
   Purpose     : Minimal, full-viewport layout for authentication pages
                 (Login, Register, Password Reset). Unlike BaseLayoutV2 and
                 MainLayoutV2, this layout renders NO application chrome:
                 - no sidebar
                 - no header
                 - no breadcrumb
                 - no grid structure

                 This ensures the auth card renders at its intended size
                 without being constrained by the main application shell.
   ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
   Changes     :
     - 1.0.0  2026-03-17  Initial implementation (V1).
     - 2.0.0  2026-03-24  Migrated to AbsenceAppV2 project structure.
     - 3.0.0  2026-04-07  Restored for V2 authentication flow after login
                          form shrink issue caused by BaseLayoutV2 grid.
                          Updated namespace to Framework.Layout.
   ===========================================================================
*@

@inherits LayoutComponentBase

@* =========================================================================
   Section: Auth shell — full-viewport wrapper for authentication pages
   ========================================================================= *@
<div class="auth-root">
    @Body
</div>
